             was indicted for <rs id="t18201028-74-off412" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18201028-74-off412" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201028-74-off412" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18201028-74-cd413" type="crimeDate">15th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201028-74-off412 t18201028-74-cd413"></join>, at St. James's, Westminster, one watch, value 10 l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201028-74-victim836" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Aldous
                        <interp inst="t18201028-74-victim836" type="surname" value="Aldous"></interp>
