                     <interp inst="t18201028-74-verdict416" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not in the dwelling-house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18201028-74-punish417" type="punishmentDescription">
